channel.title: My friend is having quite a few strange problems
channel.description:
First off, he can't run my server to host it, because he "Doesn't have any Java". He can compile it though, and he has the newest Javas. His CLASSPATH and Path variables are correct.
He can't run clients, because it tells him it can't find different parts of the client depending on the client (One can't find EGUI, another can't find client). These are all in their correct places.
Can anybody help?
Here's one picture. [img]http://i470.photobucket.com/albums/rr70/Bisaster/java.jpg[/img]
